        <item>
          <title>Fenix 7 Users Frustrated with Update Schedule - Garmin GPS Fix and ECG Support Rollout</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Garmin has rolled out a GPS fix to its Fenix 8, but some users are concerned their devices are being left behind. The company has also pushed the electrocardiogram (ECG) feature to the Fenix 7 Pro and Epix Pro Gen 2 in Europe.]]></description>
